Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: Permission denied when running tcpdump

Solution: Use sudo before tcpdump commands or add user to pcap group
Issue: Scapy import errors

Solution: Reinstall with pip3 install --upgrade scapy
Issue: No packets captured

Solution: Verify correct interface with ip addr show and check firewall rules
Issue: DNS layer not found in packets

Solution: Ensure filtering on port 53 and verify DNS traffic is present
